{"tid":2022253,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"習近平應譚德塞邀請於世界衛生大會開幕式上致辭","createTime":"2020-05-18T08:26:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-18T08:32:17.000Z","uid":205928,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2c9ba312ef803c799c22d132759c56fd9f241c0c","tid":2022253,"uid":205928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T08:26:28.000Z","msg":"習近平應譚德塞邀請於世界衛生大會開幕式上致辭<br />\n<br />\n#兩岸國際 世界衛生大會視像會議將在本港時間傍晚召開，國家主席習近平應世衛總幹事譚德塞邀請，會在開幕式上致辭。會議重點討論新型冠狀病毒疫情，歐盟及澳洲等逾百個國家提出決議，要求調查病毒源頭，檢討國際應對疫情的措施。 (5/18/16:14) 全文<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我係美國代表一定喺個gp vid call入邊搞事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50c14b9ac941241fbd5be00e89849d98290c4eeb","tid":2022253,"uid":66202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T08:32:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d952009b9134209327292a1a6ed2ee34eae43ef5","tid":2022253,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T08:32:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/fr/cp0/e15/q65/86422084_190198962322894_6931257005839482880_n.jpg?_nc_cat=105&amp;_nc_sid=110474&amp;_nc_ohc=9pBvdrIOZh8AX-8DY2N&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg1-1.fna&amp;_nc_tp=14&amp;oh=f99478c583f14954a968301d858b7726&amp;oe=5EE6D228\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Ffr%2Fcp0%2Fe15%2Fq65%2F86422084_190198962322894_6931257005839482880_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D105%26_nc_sid%3D110474%26_nc_ohc%3D9pBvdrIOZh8AX-8DY2N%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg1-1.fna%26_nc_tp%3D14%26oh%3Df99478c583f14954a968301d858b7726%26oe%3D5EE6D228&h=faed8617&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}